<font color="#FF0000">HUMBLE IN THEIR SHADOW</font><br>
<tt>Tue Dec 23 16:13:57 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
It matters little who we are or why we come only that we hear the voices of our fallen brothers.  It is a monument to our brothers when they have touched someone in such a manner.  To be touched by them in suc a way is all their loves ones could ever ask.<br><br>
I am privileged to have read the powerful words of my brothers.  Pictures have been painted that will be displayed in my mind always. 
